    "updated_at": "2017-03-08T12:32:11Z",
    "body": "I am not sure why you get like a ghost behind, but window shadow is rendered once on show. Turn it off if you don't want it. You could create larger window and use box-shadow or SVG inside of browser to render your own shadow around custom shape.\r\n\r\n```js\r\nBrowserWindow({ hasShadow: false });\r\n```"
